headline: Tractor Supply Expands Field & Stream Lineup to Celebrate Life Outdoors
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., November 04, 2025--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, announced today that its assortment of exclusive Field & Stream products has arrived. A full lineup of hunting gear and equipment, premium dog products and apparel and accessories is now available in stores and online at TractorSupply.com/FieldandStream.
